Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I understand the circumstances now.\NIt's tough being a high-school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd get ecstatic if I scolded you, Sakuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems not giving a punishment\Nis a punishment in your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not sitting right with me,\Nfor some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You hate lies like pretending\Nto be dating, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone would like lies\Nof this sort...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's not sitting right with me.\NWhat are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I've been getting excited\Nlooking at your legs for the past few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I already knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry and spit it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koga said the same thing\Nas when Kaede first stopped going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That she was embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wouldn't have a place in her class\Nif her friends found out Maesawa asked her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't want to be embarrassed\Nabout people thinking she's a loner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I talk seriously, and that's your reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't complain if you bring up\Nthe bit about your little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you off the hook this one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Simply letting you go\Nwon't do much for the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so show enough faith to be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should at least think of that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what the!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm showing some faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's your libido!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then how about a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can go look at the hydrangea\Nin Kamakura next Sunday—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in Kagoshima for a week,\Nfilming a drama starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kagoshima? I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not there for a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. You can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They gave me the outfit I wore\Nduring a fashion magazine shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I should treat this as a substitute for you\Nwhile you're in Kagoshima?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's for your sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be 15 this year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe dressing up will spark\Na little interest in leaving the house
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy that\Nyou're looking out for Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fetch her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:03:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not what you think.\NI wasn't pretending to be a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were just eavesdropping on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it works out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is from Mai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've never worn anything like this,\Nso it's embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should thank Mai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can Kaede call you "Mai-san", too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.\NAnd I'll call you "Kaede-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you thanking me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since Kaede spoke\Nwith anyone other than me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,since she's cooped up at home for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you're so honest,\Nit's not worth toying with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope "pretend" doesn't turn into "serious."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That first-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going on a date\Nafter work tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My heart is only for Mai-san,\Nso it'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get it, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JUNE 29th
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kunimi, there's a guy named Maesawa\Non the basketball team, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Oh, you mean Yosuke-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of guy is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's probably the best\Nbasketball player at our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, he's pretty popular with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep giving me more info\Nso I can hate him even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to explain, but if he's\Na good person, it'll haunt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't want\Nto badmouth people too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but yesterday, coming back from practice,\Nhe was saying he'll dump his girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because she wasn't giving it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, he has a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He does.\NSome third-year from another school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And he says a lot of demeaning things\Nabout his past girlfriends, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Makes me think how I don't want\Nto end up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the valuable info.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now it won't haunt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is all red.\NAnd you're five minutes late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I couldn't help it.\NI had to get ready and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you sure are cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me I'm cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Minus points for not wearing a miniskirt,\Nbut since you have bare legs,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't look at just my legs, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, your ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:07:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about telling you I was gonna be late,\Nbut I never got your ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a smartphone,\Nnor a flip-phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\NI dun git dat at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do you live!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do people without smartphones die?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Starting off with a yawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't slept much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're looking forward to the date?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was with everyone in the group chat\Ntill past 2AM yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I watched funny animal videos,\Nuntil I noticed it was morning already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That, and preparing for the date a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you hurry and get sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else was awake,\Nso I couldn't go to sleep before them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can watch funny animal videos\Nwhen you have time to kill, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone said they already saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in trouble if I can't join in\Non the conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rena-chan recommended them, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rena-chan again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right! My impressions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes look dead, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So they're always dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}For our closing act, we'll be attempting\Na dive from the springboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That penguin over there\Nis a bit like you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It looks like one's sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We'll have this one give it his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then are you that\Nenergetic penguin over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Actually, the penguins become so engrossed\Nin eating that they often slip and fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the penguin that follows the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Now, here we go. Three... Two... One...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It has a big butt, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was being serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It looks like he's finally gotten up,\Nbut the show's over now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's fine with everyone laughing at him.\NJust like you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't like this back in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bumpkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't want to show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you the one who showed me it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad got relocated,\Nso I ended up moving here from Fukuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was in an unnoticed group in class,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought, in Tokyo, they'd say I wasn't cool,\Nwouldn't make friends and get bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I did some research.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wore makeup for the first time,\Nand got my hair done at a fancy salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bought and wore clothes\Nfrom fashion magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I worked on my accent, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this is what I ended up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not like who you are right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I like it. I like it a whole lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then why agonize over it?\NIt's bothersome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're just being immature, thinking like\N"This isn't who I really am," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- It's annoying.\N- You're horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who you were before,\Nhow you look right now is who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter the reason, you ended up that way\Nbecause you wanted to and worked for it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you like who you are now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you say, "This isn't who I really am"?\NThat's even more messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a bit frustrated,\Nbecause I feel like you talked me into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, next is Enoshima, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A classmate, Yoneyama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yoneyama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-And "came full circle and acceptable" senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That sentiment really is spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look for it with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're in Kashiba's group, Koga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's faster if the three of us look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You heard Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for a phone strap.\NMy friends and I got matching ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It has a jellyfish charm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure you dropped it\Nsomewhere around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, I'm not sure of that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai is a strange guy, but he's not scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold on—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Koga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JUNE 30th
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want some mandarin oranges?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's against school rules\Nto leave campus during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't want it, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can do the "say aah" thing, if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to eat that way, so no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Senpai. Why did you go along\Nwith my unreasonable requests?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were desperate\Nwhen you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you hardly know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We did kick each other's butts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, I'm asking a serious question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I did think you were\Na good girl back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And because you're cute, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you go, joking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'd do the same\Nif you were ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guys are just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you would have, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a cold, just stay home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay home, I won't be able\Nto keep up with everyone's conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After just a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That one day is life-threatening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same if you're sleeping\Nin the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I'm worried about everyone's opinion\Nof me since I'm in the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're excessively self-conscious, Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the strange one, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone looks at you funny\Nand makes fun of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How are you okay like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I live\Nfor all of humanity to like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want everyone to like me.\NOr rather, I don't want them to hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if I only had one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the whole world hated me,\NI could keep living if that person needed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. A thank-you gift for a couple days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why canned peaches?\NBecause you have a peach-shaped butt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No more perversion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll savor this tonight,\Nimagining it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You dummy!\NI'm telling you, my butt isn't that big!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, no need to be humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't sound right, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, how did things\Nwith Sakurajima-senpai turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still no reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, she hasn't rejected you yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that whole loop thing didn't happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she'd say it's okay for us to start dating\Nduring lunch break that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- You're kidding.\N- It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about Sakurajima-senpai here!\NShe's in show-biz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did she say she loved you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She... hasn't said that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's just you, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I ask her out,\NI'll try my best for her to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Mai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought you might want to hear my voice,\Nso I called you for your sake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was just thinking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope you have your underwear on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though it's natural for you\Nto do things like that thinking about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm buck naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm kidding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just got out of a bath,\Nso I'm only wearing underware.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell such stupid lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I might be indebted to you\Non restless nights, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, yeah, do as you wish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, how are things over there?\NWas the date with your cute little girlfriend fun?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In a way, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was the right answer to that question?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about bolting out of your house\Nand coming down to Kagoshima to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And when I do,\NI need to hug you buck naked, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a mood killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san, is the filming fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any jobs you want to do, Sakuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think I want\Nto be Santa Claus in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because he doesn't work\N364 days out of the year?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Say dumb things and you'll become dumb!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JULY 5th
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kunimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuta's not in the classroom,\Nso I was wondering if he was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he with that first-year?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let Azusagawa know if he shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba, you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot!? You must be an idiot!\NDon't be oddly considerate of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kunimi will catch on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he was going to notice with that,\Nhe would've caught on long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...to your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You guys seem to be busy,\Nso I'll talk to you later, Sakuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He really was handsome as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, what does Azusagawa\Nthe not-so-handsome rascal want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't relived the same day since then,\Nso I was wondering what it actually was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's exactly what you said it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The first-year that is your\Nsupposed girlfriend was Laplace's Demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She kept rolling the dice until\Na future convenient to her occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's satisfied with her current condition,\Nthere's no need to relive it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she's not aware of it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she was, that'd probably\Nmake her a real demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kamisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I said this before,\Nabout not getting close to Yuuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:17:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think what you said was,\N"Don't talk to him."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That, and what's with the girl\Nin the physics lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is she to Yuuma?\NThey seem to be chatting often.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ask Kunimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're friends with her too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so irritated?\NYou constipated?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die! Just die right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are the pits!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get some dietary fiber!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JULY 6th
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kunimi, it's annoying, so I'll say this up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your girlfriend picked a fight\Nwith me again yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really have to choose\Nbetween me or her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is that not-so-ultimate ultimatum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll call her tonight about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Sakuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is the thing about you dating Koga for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's more like a trial period.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:18:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I should have mentioned this yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's about Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are bad rumors about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like how she's easy, a whore,\Nscrewing you all the time, stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found out from\Nthe basketball team's group messages, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuta, you asked about Yosuke-senpai\Nthe other day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Futaba, do you ever have thoughts like,\N"What if, back then..."?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For you, that would be about your little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not bad,\Nbut I'd say it's not like you to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I really want\Nto do everything over, per se.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to stop thinking about "what if's",\Nsince it's useless to think about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:19:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That IS like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Futaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would I have a chance of winning
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,against someone who's not only bigger than me,\Nbut works out on an athletic team?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Humans aren't ordinary monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you can win if you used your brains?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Mai Sakurajima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just got back from Kagoshima.\NThought I'd let you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JULY 7th
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I totally messed up my bangs!\NIsn't it like terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't have such a morbid look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First-years nowadays get it on often, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you laugh at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still laughing. What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You messing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm just making fun of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ya wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not being fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that'd be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who isn't cool!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should go wash your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I stepped on some poop yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one messing with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to attract attention,\Ndon't do stupid stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your way of life is so uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have to say one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Getting screwed all the time?\NGimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a virgin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wai— Sen—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, that's going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was going way too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I understand a bit\Nof what you said before, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the whole world was your enemy,\Nif one person needs you kinda thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Kinda thing?"\NAt least remember things properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really felt like I was your girlfriend.\NLike I was being cherished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I promised you that I would for the first term.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You normally wouldn't go so far\Nfor the sake of a fake girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a perfectionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Mega lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even tell dat?\NI meant boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's from Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She wrote, "I'm so disappointed\Nin Maesawa-senpai."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If some poop on his face makes her lose interest,\Nher admiration was just that superficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's something I'd like to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Bathroom break?\N- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...never done anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still a virgin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're so horrible for laughing at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.18,0:22:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You thought I'd really believe a rumor like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't, but I'd feel bad if you did, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't you say you used\Nto have a boyfriend at some point?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, everyone said they had boyfriends\Nback in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And they were like, "Of course you had one too,\Nright Tomoe?" kinda thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I said I never dated anyone,\NI thought you'd make a fool out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are you fighting, Koga?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How should I pay you back for all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when all the lies are over,\Nyou can be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're hopeless, so I'll be your best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.01,0:24:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of you, Sakuta.\NYou're such a rascal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.01,0:25:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Time\N#6 This World You Chose
